To launch rover robot and move_base:

Check ports. sudo chmod 0777 /dev/ttyUSB0/1
1) Launch rover driver:
roslaunch roverrobotics_driver pro.launch

2) Launch lidar:
roslaunch rplidar_ros view_rplidar.launch

3) Launch robot description:
roslaunch roverrobotics_description description-4wd.launch

4) Publish odom -> base_footprint transform:
python2 odom_baselink.py

5) Start slam_mapping:
rosrun gmapping slam_gmapping _base_frame:=base_footprint _linearUpdate:=0.0 _angularUpdate:=0.0

6) Start move_base:
rosrun move_base move_base _base_local_planner:=dwa_local_planner/DWAPlannerROS

Now you are ready to go!!!



